nd he slips. He said, Mr East, he said, that'll be my downfall, he said, I'll slip and I'll die. So I says, well Doctor, I said, you're a fine Job's comforter. I said - a true story, I said, there's only you and I on the road, I said, and you're talking t
o me like that. So he never said no more, after that. And when we got in the surgery - bang went that door. Yes. An older man }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3610574\charrsid11870673 he}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1983454\charrsid11870673  was.
