\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4136265 WE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1983454\charrsid11870673 Yes. She had 'em home. She had 'em at ho
me. Yes. And - 'course those days it used to be - thirty-one and six. Thirty shillings for the - doctor, and the midwife you give her the eighteenpence.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2764714 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1983454\charrsid11870673 And she was the one who did all the work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4136265 WE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1983454\charrsid11870673 Done all the work. Well then - yes - then - I was 
standing again the gate there, and his son come along. And he, you know, they were star turns, you know of course how you get all hot and bothered, so I said - excuse me sir, I said, are you the doctor? He said, who are you? So I said, I'm Mr. East. Oh he
 
said, I'm going up to your house. I said, do you mind hurrying up? He said, why? Oh, he said, it's only, he said, these things, he said, they take their time. Of course we lived in the second floor in G block. So of course up the stairs we go, 'course I c
ouldn't go in. 'Cos the wife was in the kitchen, we used to have the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3610574\charrsid11870673 bed in}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1983454\charrsid11870673  the kitchen, because of the old fire. He come out, he said - give us a fag. I used to smoke Weights in those days. So I give him a fag. So he said, what did I tell you?
