No. And he never told us who he voted for. No. I'd say to him, dad who did you vote for? That's me own business, Bill. So I never used to ask him after that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2764714 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1983454\charrsid11870673 What about your mother, was she ever interested in politics?
