't used to go out at all because when I was married we - we'd be broke on Sunday, never used to go out at all, and - as I say we heard the horses and - police on the old horses going by, when - of course we was A block at the time, and - that was our life
. Yes. That was a terrible - thing that was with Mosely's }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3610574\charrsid11870673 crowd}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1983454\charrsid11870673 
, terrible.
