\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3610574\charrsid11870673 trying}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1983454\charrsid11870673  to - of course you used to have th
e outside - outside the docks you'd have meetings and all that, of course if a man was interested he'd stop, and if he wasn't - he would walk on.
