No. No. That's one thing he said to me, Bill, when you go to work - he said, if you fancy a - bet - see a coalman, his old horse and van, true story, or else a man with a hors
e and van, he said, if you do, he said, give him your shilling what you was going to give to the - bookmaker, and he'll let you back that horse and van down any gateway - you like, now that is a real true story. Yes. And that's - but he liked his beer but
 he never gambled. No. And I - I never gambled meself.
