\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3610574\charrsid11870673 theatres}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1983454\charrsid11870673  or concerts or music halls, or to cinema when you were a small boy?
